README

Goals of the project

- Create projects using spring-boot
- Simple CRUD using JPA
- Integration of JPA with hibernate/MYSQL
o Integration of JPA with postgresql
o JPA relationships (1-1, 1-M, M-M)
o JPA in the context of inheritance/composition
o Creation of multiple standalone (micro?)services from single codebase (if this is desirable)
o Collaboration of services via some kind of integration bus
o Security token management across services
o Horizontal scalability / fault tolerance of services (spring-cloud??)
o UI via Vaadin
o unit/integration testing of autowired spring components (eg how to test persistence)